Some ideas for creating a NeuroML v2.0 based Python API using code generated from the XML Schema for v2.0:
http://sourceforge.net/apps/trac/neuroml/browser/NeuroML2/Schemas/NeuroML2/NeuroML_v2alpha.xsd
using a (modified version of) generateDS.py:
http://www.rexx.com/~dkuhlman/generateDS.html

To install/test:

Run: 
  sudo python setup.py install
then test with:
  python readNml2.py
  python writeNml2.py


Notes:

The generated Python classes use camelCase(!!). 

Almost no helper functions are present, just the default attribute/child element get/add/set functions from generateDS.py.


